### GitHub Upload & Vercel Deploy

1.  Is pure folder ko **GitHub Repository** mein upload karein.
2.  **Vercel.com** par jayen, Login karein.
3.  **"Add New Project"** click karein aur GitHub se apni Repo select karein.
4.  **Deploy** par click karein. Aapki app live ho jayegi!
